data.name: FormComponentType
desc: These constants specify the class types used to identify a component.

items.name: CONTROL
lines: This generic identifier is for controls which cannot be identified by another specific identifier.

items.name: COMMANDBUTTON
lines: specifies a control that is used to begin, interrupt, or end a process.

items.name: RADIOBUTTON
lines: specifies a control that acts like a radio button.
Grouped together, such radio buttons present a set of two or more mutually exclusive choices to the user.

items.name: IMAGEBUTTON
lines: specifies a control that displays an image that responds to mouse clicks.

items.name: CHECKBOX
lines: specifies a control that is used to check or uncheck to turn an option on or off.

items.name: LISTBOX
lines: specifies a control that displays a list from which the user can select one or more items.

items.name: COMBOBOX
lines: specifies a control that is used when a list box combined with a static text control or an edit control is needed.

items.name: GROUPBOX
lines: specifies a control that displays a frame around a group of controls with or without a caption.

items.name: TEXTFIELD
lines: specifies a control that is a text component that allows for the editing of a single line of text.

items.name: FIXEDTEXT
lines: specifies a control to display a fixed text, usually used to label other controls.

items.name: GRIDCONTROL
lines: is a table like control to display database data.

items.name: FILECONTROL
lines: specifies a control which can be used to enter text, extended by an (user-startable) file dialog to browse for files.

items.name: HIDDENCONTROL
lines: specifies a control that should not be visible.

items.name: IMAGECONTROL
lines: specifies a control to display an image.

items.name: DATEFIELD
lines: specifies a control to display and edit a date value.

items.name: TIMEFIELD
lines: specifies a control to display and edit a time value.

items.name: NUMERICFIELD
lines: specifies a field to display and edit a numeric value.

items.name: CURRENCYFIELD
lines: specifies a field to display and edit a currency value.

items.name: PATTERNFIELD
lines: specifies a control to display and edit a string according to a pattern.

items.name: SCROLLBAR
lines: specifies a control to display and edit, in the form of a scrollbar, a value from a continuous value range

items.name: SPINBUTTON
lines: specifies a control to edit, in the form of a spin field, a value from a continuous range of values

items.name: NAVIGATIONBAR
lines: specifies a control which provides controller functionality for the com.sun.star.form.component.DataForm it belongs to, such as functionality to navigate or filter this form.
